# Review Pipeline Comprehensive Overhaul

## Research Summary: How Review/Ranking Content Works

From analyzing the user's style analysis data and industry best practices:

### OUTLINE Level (what [system_review_outline.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_review_outline.txt) should ensure)

| Element | Best Practice | Current Status | Gap? |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Ranking criteria stated in hook** | Hook must explain HOW products are ranked | ❌ No rule | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Product selection logic** | Drop products that don't fit the angle | ✅ Done | — |
| **Ranking order by framework angle** | Framework criteria determines order | ✅ Done | — |
| **Transition design per chapter** | `ends_with` must bridge to next product's strength | ✅ Done | — |
| **Escalation tracking** | Each product must feel MORE impressive than the last | ❌ No rule | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **"Who it's for" per product** | Each product identifies its ideal user | ❌ Not in outline | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Ranking justification** | Output should include WHY each product is ranked where it is | ❌ Not in output | ✅ NEEDS FIX |

### WRITER Level (what [system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt) should ensure)

| Element | Best Practice | Current Status | Gap? |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Product chapter template** | Each body chapter follows a consistent structure | ⚠️ Framework has template but writer prompt doesn't enforce it | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Pros/Cons balance** | Cover both strengths AND weaknesses | ❌ No rule about cons | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **"Who it's for"** | End each product with who should buy it | ❌ Not in writer | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Transition execution** | Use `ends_with` from outline to create bridge | ⚠️ `ends_with` provided but no rule to USE it | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Data from blueprint ONLY** | Specs must come from blueprint, no hallucination | ⚠️ Rule 10 says "don't contradict" but not "don't invent" | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Countdown number in text** | Each chapter must explicitly state its rank | ❌ No rule | ✅ NEEDS FIX |

### CONCLUSION Level (end chapter)

| Element | Best Practice | Current Status | Gap? |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Recap by category** | "Best for budget", "Best trigger", "Best overall" | ❌ Only generic "summary verdict" | ✅ NEEDS FIX |
| **Restate ranking criteria** | Remind audience how you ranked | ❌ Missing | ✅ NEEDS FIX |

